# Git LFS — raster render outputs, scoped to keyshot/ only.
# KeyShot renders and raster texture/bump maps are raster by nature; everywhere
# else in the repo is SVG-first (see /CLAUDE.md), so these rules live here
# rather than repo-wide. Inert until a matching file is committed; run
# `git lfs install` first.
*.png  filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
*.jpg  filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
*.jpeg filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
*.tif  filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
*.tiff filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
